title: Riot kayle
body: Hey riot i already got a riot kayle before this event and now i got only icon and i didn't get mistery skin why?!?!{{champion:10}} {{champion:10}} {{champion:10}} {{champion:10}} {{sticker:zombie-brand-clap}} {{sticker:zombie-brand-mindblown}}

replies.body: Gifts are still being distributed, and it's going to be a bit before you get your mystery skin.  Use our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-) to stay up to date on the process.  Hang tight until the gifts are finished being sent out!
